Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libsane (>=1.0.23), jq, curl
Description: Simple daemon polling button presses on SANE scanners
 Insaned polls button presses on SANE scanners and executes user-defined scripts
 when a button is triggered
